text: Alexandra Jasmine Myles (born 17 October 1990) is a New Zealand water polo player. She is a member of the New Zealand women's national water polo team. She played at the 2009 World Aquatics Championships, 2011 World Aquatics Championships, and 2013 World Aquatics Championships. == References == Category:1990 births Category:New Zealand water polo players Category:Living people
